item.title: What are the reasons for me making a website?
item.description: There are many reasons for why one would want a website. In my case I’ve decided that I need a place where I can structure and store my thoughts regarding various topics rather than just let them fade away from my memory over time. Also I’ve never created a website for personal use before so that needed to change. :^)
item.content:
There are many reasons for why one would want a website.

In my case I’ve decided that I need a place where I can structure and store my thoughts regarding various topics rather than just let them fade away from my memory over time.

Also I’ve never created a website for personal use before so that needed to change. :^)
